[{"id":"VH917318","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure presents a proton on the left, with an arrow labeled v directed to the right. The proton is about to pass through an opening in a barrier. To the right of the barrier, E and B fields are shown. The E field is evenly spaced arrows pointing to the right, and the B field is a grid of evenly spaced crosses inside circles.\" height=\"265\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH917318.g01.png\" width=\"450\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A proton traveling horizontally with velocity <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Vector v\"><math alttext=\"Vector v\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>v</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>→</mo></mrow></mover></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> enters a region with a uniform electric field of magnitude <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"uppercase E\"><math alttext=\"uppercase E\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>E</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> to the right and a uniform magnetic field of magnitude <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle mathvariant=\"italic\"><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> into the page, as shown above. At the instant it enters the region, what is the magnitude and direction of the proton’s acceleration?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH917318_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction lowercase e times uppercase E over m sub p\"><math alttext=\"the fraction lowercase e times uppercase E over m sub p\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>e</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> to the right</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction lowercase e times v B over m sub p\"><math alttext=\"the fraction lowercase e times v B over m sub p\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>e</mi><mi>v</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> upward</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction lowercase e over m sub p, end sub, end fraction, times, the square root of uppercase E squared plus, open parenthesis, v B, close parenthesis, squared, end root\"><math alttext=\"the fraction lowercase e over m sub p, end sub, end fraction, times, the square root of uppercase E squared plus, open parenthesis, v B, close parenthesis, squared, end root\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>e</mi></mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></mfrac><msqrt><mrow><msup><mrow><mi>E</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>v</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></msqrt></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> diagonally up and to the right</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction lowercase e over m sub p, end sub, times, open parenthesis, uppercase E plus v B, close parenthesis\"><math alttext=\"the fraction lowercase e over m sub p, end sub, times, open parenthesis, uppercase E plus v B, close parenthesis\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>e</mi></mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></mfrac><mo>(</mo><mi>E</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>v</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> diagonally up and to the right</p>"],"answer":2}]